#dev #alpha

> Open source alpha release — current status and pending tasks.

Status: alpha. The core loop (parse → store → query → agent skills) is built
and tested. API and file format may still change.

README was rewritten to target external users — covers: why it exists, pipx
install, bootstrap quickstart (init-skills → watch → new notes → ask agent),
the 4-skill workflow, file format, command tables, and development setup.

User-facing install (requires Python 3.11+):
  pipx install git+https://github.com/gtrogers/electric-sheep-pen.git

GitHub remote: git@github.com:gtrogers/electric-sheep-pen.git (set up, not yet pushed to PyPI).

